2012-12-01  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	Release: 1.1

	* GNUmakefile (VERSION): Bump to "1.1" for release.

2012-12-01  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[int] Call ‘setlocale’ for all programs, first thing.

	* a1-nf3-guile2: ...here.
	* a2-nf3-mixp: Likewise.
	* a2ixin: Likewise.
	* retrieve: Likewise.

2012-12-01  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[slog] Sync ‘string-xrep’ from upstream.

	This is "slog" because it affects Guile 2,
	for which ‘char-set:full’ is unwieldy to filter.

	* z-fixed-pp.scm (string-xrep): Synch.

2012-12-01  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[int] a2ixin: Inline ‘xnode!’-derived procs.

	* a2ixin (node-name, node-next, node-prev, node-up): Delete.
	(in): Use ‘(xnode! 'nodename)’ directly.
	(in grok): Map ‘xnode!’ over ‘nodenext’, ‘nodeprev’, ‘nodeup’.

2012-12-01  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	Fix bug: Apply ‘(ice-9 pretty-print)’ fix more/less deeply.

	* z-fixed-pp.scm (obj->string): New proc.
	(generic-write wr): Replace "string w/ ‘write’" case
	with more ‘(not display?)’ case, using ‘obj->string’ there;
	update ‘else’ case to no longer check for ‘(not display?)’.

2012-11-30  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	Include .sxml and .ixin files in dist.

	* GNUmakefile (dist): Add to prereq list all ‘$(hmm)’-based
	.sxml and .ixin files; include ‘$^’ in cp(1) command.

2012-11-29  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	Release: 1.0

	* GNUmakefile (VERSION): Bump to "1.0" for release.


